Use Case: Harvester
Short description: Harvester is the main program that controlls the parser. User presses one of the buttons, and then starts one of the following: UC_Startparser, UC_StopParser

Priority: High

Extends or Includes: UC_Startparser, UC_StopParser, UC_ExportLog, UC_PrintStatus, UC_ClearLog

Participating actors: User, Harvester

Normal flow of events:

User                                    System
----                                    ------
The user clicks on a button

													      						Harvester lanches the UC associated with the button.

User closes Harvester.

					Harvester stops.

